    <abstract>
      <t>   This document specifies use of the SIGZERO and SIG(0) Domain Name
   System (DNS) Resource Records (RRs) to provide public key based
   authentication of DNS requests and transactions.  This document
   obsoletes RFC 2931.

	 </t>
